    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, practical choice for those who value function over form. While the engine and transmission are operational and the car is roadworthy, it does show noticeable signs of wear, including some exterior blemishes and an interior that could use a deep clean. It has been a dependable driver, though it would benefit from some upcoming routine maintenance to keep it in peak working order. This is a solid option for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that gets the job done.",
